Copies of the documentation for each release are placed
on the Bedework website in PDF and HTML format at
http://www.bedework.org/bedework/update.do?artcenterkey=22
(for the current release) and in each release directory at
http://www.bedework.org/bedework/update.do?artcenterkey=48

Documentation for Bedework is maintained in Open Document
book format as the "Bedework Manual".  These files can be
opened with Open Office and are found in the bedework/docs/book
directory.
